text: Mihaela Guma (born 18 October 1993) is a Moldovan footballer who plays as a midfielder and a defender. She has been a member of the Moldova women's national team. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Moldovan women's footballers Category:Moldova women's international footballers
